sets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />祝福東涌人"},{"pid":"1080cff35db14b7a087e5b16ce230342594d30af","tid":1863142,"uid":47905,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T05:44:46.000Z","msg":"典型奴隸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n覺得自己好有責任心<br />\n但其實呢類人係被中共洗左腦既奴隸<br />\n<br />\n香港太多呢類人<br />\n實屬可悲"},{"pid":"1141aae81824bc6fabb9a6ceed1b07d7fb3046bd","tid":1863142,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:41:09.000Z","msg":"俾錯正皮<br />\n個肺都纖維化埋仲同個政權搵命搏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}